  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Effortless Outfit Changes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Switch between professional assistant attire, starry evening gowns, beach swimwear... Diverse styles, defined by you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/5bc36722c46ece40d8e91e920e742d1f.poster.avif?t=1770369377\" width=800 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/5bc36722c46ece40d8e91e920e742d1f.webm?t=1770369377\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/5bc36722c46ece40d8e91e920e742d1f.mp4?t=1770369377\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dye System</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supports dyeing for hairstyles and clothing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/66aa5fc4baf9a0bbd53f555ab23754d6.avif?t=1770369377\" width=1600 height=788 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Character Interaction</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple interactive modes blend emotional companionship with practical features, creating a desktop elf that serves as both an efficiency tool and a virtual partner.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Basic Interactions </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/8da04f4bf4fe7022f6f4cf740bf304aa.poster.avif?t=1770369377\" width=800 height=576 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/8da04f4bf4fe7022f6f4cf740bf304aa.webm?t=1770369377\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/8da04f4bf4fe7022f6f4cf740bf304aa.mp4?t=1770369377\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/517f174c90717127fc259b06e95179ba.poster.avif?t=1770369377\" width=800 height=576 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/517f174c90717127fc259b06e95179ba.webm?t=1770369377\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/517f174c90717127fc259b06e95179ba.mp4?t=1770369377\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Functional Interactions (Use items, Access utilities)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/904c1c62ef24017a845da867a5740bc0.poster.avif?t=1770369377\" width=800 height=574 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/904c1c62ef24017a845da867a5740bc0.webm?t=1770369377\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/904c1c62ef24017a845da867a5740bc0.mp4?t=1770369377\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/ccecbcc8246887635047bb7d89943ffb.poster.avif?t=1770369377\" width=800 height=574 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/ccecbcc8246887635047bb7d89943ffb.webm?t=1770369377\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/ccecbcc8246887635047bb7d89943ffb.mp4?t=1770369377\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story Quests</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An immersive gaming experience that lets you delve deeper into your desktop elf world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/90a11f3f3dc5b71a894e205734dde7af.poster.avif?t=1770369377\" width=800 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/90a11f3f3dc5b71a894e205734dde7af.webm?t=1770369377\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/90a11f3f3dc5b71a894e205734dde7af.mp4?t=1770369377\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Creative Workshop Support</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Freely upload/download Mods to enrich your gameplay~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Workshop supports adding/modifying:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Character models</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Costume textures</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dialogues, voice lines & animations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >AI Chat</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/872b448cdd6494720f298566305f2cae.avif?t=1770369377\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras_big/872b448cdd6494720f298566305f2cae.avif?t=1770369377 width=800 height=454 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/c5d915a3d004c666831385492abb3c63.poster.avif?t=1770369377\" width=800 height=534 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/c5d915a3d004c666831385492abb3c63.webm?t=1770369377\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003300/extras/c5d915a3d004c666831385492abb3c63.mp4?t=1770369377\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tap for reactions, converse with emotional intelligence, customize looks to express yourself - This desktop elf is both a task-organizing assistant and an empathetic partner who understands your moods.</strong></p>",
